<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Media - Dr. Shahida Pervin</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&family=Roboto:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2c3e50;
            --secondary: #2980b9;
            --bg-light: #f7f9fa;
            --white: #fff;
            --accent: #e67e22;
        }
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        header {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 32px 0 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(44,62,80,0.07);
        }
        .nav-links {
            margin-top: 18px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 28px;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--white);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            padding-bottom: 3px;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
        }
        main {
            margin-top: 120px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 42px;
            padding: 32px 18px;
        }
        .content-section {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(44,62,80,0.09);
            padding: 36px 32px 32px 32px;
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .content-section h1 {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .content-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-top: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .content-section p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .media-link-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--secondary);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            margin-top: 16px;
            transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
            border: 2px solid var(--secondary);
        }
        .media-link-btn:hover {
            background: var(--accent);
            border-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        footer {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 16px 0;
            margin-top: auto;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            main {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 20px;
                margin-top: 110px;
            }
            .content-section {
                min-width: unset;
                max-width: 98vw;
                width: 98vw;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header {
                padding: 18px 0 8px 0;
            }
            main {
                padding: 14px 5px;
                margin-top: 90px;
            }
            .content-section {
                padding: 22px 16px 22px 16px;
            }
            .content-section h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 12px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .nav-links a {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div style="font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;">
            Dr. Shahida Pervin
        </div>
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="index.html">Home</a>
            <a href="About.html">About me</a>
            <a href="Research.html">Research</a>
            <a href="Teaching.html">Teaching</a>
            <a href="Media.html">Media</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="content-section">
            <h1>Media & Gallery</h1>
            <p>
                Welcome to my media gallery. Here you'll find a collection of images, presentations, and other multimedia content related to my academic and professional work.
            </p>
            
            <h2>View Full Gallery</h2>
            <p>
                For a comprehensive collection of my media content, including photos, event coverage, and multimedia materials, please visit my dedicated media page:
            </p>
            <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/shahida-pervin/media?authuser=0" target="_blank" class="media-link-btn">
                View Media Gallery →
            </a>
            
            <h2>About This Section</h2>
            <p>
                This section features various media materials from my academic career, including:
            </p>
            <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Professional photographs and portraits</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Conference presentations and event photos</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Academic workshop documentation</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Media appearances and interviews</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        © 2025 Shahida Pervin | All Rights Reserved
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
